{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"dying-verastile-quelea","description":"## Reproduction Steps\n1. Merge a change to infra/scripts/observability.sh (e.g. change 491's root_disk_used_percent section) and let autodeploy roll /opt/rebar forward.\n2. autodeploy materialises compose/config but never re-runs infra/scripts/install-observability.sh, which is the only thing that copies observability.sh to /usr/local/bin/rebar-observability.sh (the path the systemd timer executes).\n3. The timer keeps running the stale copy.\n\n**Expected:** landing an observability change on main reaches the box's running probe on the next deploy. **Actual:** /usr/local/bin/rebar-observability.sh was a Jun 30 copy (7,196 bytes) while /opt/rebar held 16,275 bytes — the deploy_errors (4d), merge-change (4c) and root-disk (2b) metric sections silently never ran in prod. Found 2026-07-10 verifying ac14; remediated one-off by re-running install-observability.sh via SSM. This is the same drift class as incident 2731 (provisioning script not extended with the artifact it must manage), one layer up: the deploy loop does not own installer-materialized artifacts.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] autodeploy's materialise step refreshes /usr/local/bin/rebar-observability.sh when infra/scripts/observability.sh changes (re-run install-observability.sh, or install the file directly like other materialised artifacts).\n- [ ] A drift check (config-check or a test) fails when the materialised copy can go stale — i.e. the install path is derived from one source of truth, mirroring the b005 --print-volumes pattern.\n- [ ] Evidence on the box post-deploy: /usr/local/bin/rebar-observability.sh matches /opt/rebar/infra/scripts/observability.sh after an autodeploy run.\n- [ ] File paths: infra/scripts/autodeploy.sh, infra/scripts/install-observability.sh.","id":"1d63-430a-1a70-4987","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"autodeploy never refreshes installer-materialized host scripts — /usr/local/bin/rebar-observability.sh went 10 days stale"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783703080920077001,"uuid":"db5d353a-9e15-49a6-a9b1-48b1593a9baf"}